          <blockquote>
              <p>The Flocculent Cathedral module from <a href="https://www.drivethrurpg.com/product/284862/Codex--Hunger-Apr-2019" rel="nofollow noopener">Codex - Hunger</a> reminded me of <em>Annihilation</em>. The default setting for Trophy is fantasy so I think more modern character gen stuff would really help to give the book’s flavor. Also, an Actual Play will soon be on a Gauntlet podcast!</p>
